    "date": "2020-10-27T19:54:06Z",
    "text": "Transparency in Chinese Government Investment Act of 2020\n\n This bill requires an issuer of securities to disclose in certain annual reports and in an initial public offering involvement with China. Specifically, issuers must report participation in certain Chinese policies or plans, financial support from China, and certain individuals' involvement with the Chinese government."
